extends layouts/main

block content
  .container(style="padding: 4rem 2rem; max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;")
    h1(style="font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--gray-900); margin-bottom: 2rem;") Privacy Policy
    p(style="color: var(--gray-500); margin-bottom: 2rem;") Last updated: December 2025
    
    .policy-content(style="line-height: 1.8; color: var(--gray-700);")
      h2(style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--gray-900); margin: 2rem 0 1rem;") 1. Information We Collect
      p We collect information you provide directly to us, such as when you create an account, make a booking, submit a review, or contact us for support. This may include:
      ul(style="margin: 1rem 0 1rem 2rem;")
        li Name, email address, and phone number
        li Profile information and preferences
        li Payment and billing information
        li Booking history and communications
        li Device and usage information
      
      h2(style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--gray-900); margin: 2rem 0 1rem;") 2. How We Use Your Information
      p We use the information we collect to:
      ul(style="margin: 1rem 0 1rem 2rem;")
        li Process your bookings and payments
        li Communicate with you about your reservations
        li Provide customer support
        li Send promotional communications (with your consent)
        li Improve our services and develop new features
        li Ensure the security of our platform
      
      h2(style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--gray-900); margin: 2rem 0 1rem;") 3. Information Sharing
      p We may share your information with:
      ul(style="margin: 1rem 0 1rem 2rem;")
        li Hosts or guests to facilitate bookings
        li Payment processors for secure transactions
        li Service providers who assist our operations
        li Law enforcement when required by law
      p We do not sell your personal information to third parties.
      
      h2(style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--gray-900); margin: 2rem 0 1rem;") 4. Data Security
      p We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. This includes encryption, secure servers, and regular security assessments.
      
      h2(style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--gray-900); margin: 2rem 0 1rem;") 5. Your Rights
      p You have the right to:
      ul(style="margin: 1rem 0 1rem 2rem;")
        li Access and update your personal information
        li Request deletion of your account and data
        li Opt out of marketing communications
        li Request a copy of your data
      
      h2(style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--gray-900); margin: 2rem 0 1rem;") 6. Cookies
      p We use cookies and similar technologies to enhance your experience, analyze usage patterns, and deliver personalized content. You can manage your cookie preferences through your browser settings.
      
      h2(style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--gray-900); margin: 2rem 0 1rem;") 7. Contact Us
      p If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
      p(style="margin-top: 1rem;")
        strong Email: 
        | privacy@easetrip.my
      p
        strong Address: 
        | EaseTrip Sdn Bhd, Level 10, Menara KLCC, Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia
